### ── 12. RUN LIVE INFRASTRUCTURE LOCATION DISCHARGE FILE (PATCH) ─────────────
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/indoor-patient/{{createdPatientId}}/discharge
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "note": "Discharge parameters stable. Medications and post-op care directives handed over to family."
}

###


### ── 13. DATA RETENTION ENTRIES SOFT-DELETE PROFILE (DELETE) ─────────────────
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/indoor-patient/{{createdPatientId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}